                            <comment id="13773651" author="jmspaggi" created="Sat, 21 Sep 2013 00:59:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;People will LOVE that! &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That will also go with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7769&quot; title=&quot;Checksum and shortcurcuit status in UI&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-7769&quot;&gt;HBASE-7769&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14165766" author="stack" created="Thu, 9 Oct 2014 21:22:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Let me do this too in same way I did &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12220&quot; title=&quot;Add hedgedReads and hedgedReadWins metrics&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-12220&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-12220&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (This is &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=srikanth235&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;srikanth235&quot;&gt;Srikanth Srungarapu&lt;/a&gt;&apos;s idea).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14166003" author="stack" created="Thu, 9 Oct 2014 23:44:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;NVM.  Can&apos;t do it w/ same &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12220&quot; title=&quot;Add hedgedReads and hedgedReadWins metrics&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-12220&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-12220&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; technique.  DFSIS ReadStatistics are per instance rather than a shared static.  Would be a bit of work collecting up these stats across all open streams.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14326984" author="otis" created="Thu, 19 Feb 2015 04:38:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Isn&apos;t this a dupe of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8868&quot; title=&quot;add metric to report client shortcircuit reads&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-8868&quot;&gt;HBASE-8868&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14327353" author="jmspaggi" created="Thu, 19 Feb 2015 12:39:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sound like is... &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8868&quot; title=&quot;add metric to report client shortcircuit reads&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-8868&quot;&gt;HBASE-8868&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7769&quot; title=&quot;Checksum and shortcurcuit status in UI&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-7769&quot;&gt;HBASE-7769&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9604&quot; title=&quot;Add metric on short-circuit reads&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-9604&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-9604&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; might be regrouped under a single one...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14330015" author="stack" created="Sat, 21 Feb 2015 05:53:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Dup of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8868&quot; title=&quot;add metric to report client shortcircuit reads&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-8868&quot;&gt;HBASE-8868&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
